    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/b97dda049268813d36b5db64d9cf56d7.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/b97dda049268813d36b5db64d9cf56d7.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/b97dda049268813d36b5db64d9cf56d7.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>准备好迎接《忍者猴》的激烈战斗吧，在这款游戏中，你将控制一个灵活的忍者猴，在与致命蜜蜂的史诗战斗中大展身手！这款刺激的 Roguelike 平台游戏将带你踏上一段生存、策略和忍者技能的旅程，每个决定都至关重要。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><br><strong>⚔️ 紧张的战斗:</strong><br><br>在令人惊叹的横向卷轴平台环境中，与无情的蜜蜂浪潮作斗争。生存每一轮，并从三种独特的升级中选择，以强化你的忍者猴，为下一次挑战做好准备。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/233faffc58c721a2f7600fe33324165c.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/233faffc58c721a2f7600fe33324165c.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/233faffc58c721a2f7600fe33324165c.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>💥 挑战首领:</strong><br><br>测试你对强大首领的技能，这些首领需要高级策略和快速反应。击败他们以继续前进，发现新的奖励和秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/9be169b62bb419a342a12ad5e6f8861b.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/9be169b62bb419a342a12ad5e6f8861b.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/9be169b62bb419a342a12ad5e6f8861b.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🔄 进度与升级:</strong><br><br>在你的旅程中解锁各种升级、职业、地图、武器和能力。每一个选择都塑造了你忍者猴的构建，允许独特的组合和个性化的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/afdb4b21fa660ef71c80ca47f79405af.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/afdb4b21fa660ef71c80ca47f79405af.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/afdb4b21fa660ef71c80ca47f79405af.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🗺️ 游戏模式:</strong><br><br>探索不同的地图，每张地图都有自己独特的挑战和环境。在每张地图上面对100轮，随着你进度的提升，难度和敌人的多样性也会增加。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/f5cab88653c050ae7c07356aab907403.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/f5cab88653c050ae7c07356aab907403.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/f5cab88653c050ae7c07356aab907403.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🤸‍♂️ 平台技能:</strong><br><br>利用自动攻击，专注于掌握平台技能并避免致命的危险。跳跃、奔跑和闪避，以在蜜蜂的混乱中生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/af718b13a5368ce3bb4f69449d8105ab.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/af718b13a5368ce3bb4f69449d8105ab.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/af718b13a5368ce3bb4f69449d8105ab.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🎮 上瘾的游戏玩法:</strong><br><br>凭借流畅且令人上瘾的游戏机制，《忍者猴》为各种类型的玩家提供了一个令人兴奋且有回报的体验。提升你的技能，自定义你的构建，争取成为终极忍者猴。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/7a4969701f6557cfe758708e99f0cafa.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/7a4969701f6557cfe758708e99f0cafa.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备好战斗:</strong></h2><br>《忍者猴》不仅仅是一个平台游戏——它是对你的战略技能和快速反应的考验。你准备好迎接挑战了吗？加入战斗，击败蜜蜂群体，证明你是史上最强的忍者猴！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>现在添加到愿望单！</strong></h2><br>不要错过这个史诗般的冒险机会。将《忍者猴》添加到你在 Steam 的愿望单中，成为第一批体验游戏震撼动作的玩家！",
